VAT £ inc.VAT Options Colour: Black Back Panel White Back Panel Clear Back Panel Clear Frost Back Panel Coloured Back Panel 2: 2: Qty Add to basket Get a quote Staff Photo Notice Boards - Perspex Acrylic Staff photo notice boards, or "Meet The Team" boards are a perfect way of letting people know who's who in a school, NHS Wards, general office and commercial workplace, recreation centres, reception areas, etc. Each clear pocket allows a small photo of a relevent member of staff. Options available include: choice of back acrylic colour, the number of photo pockets. We also offer a secure, tamper proof version, please click here for further details. NEW! We can now offer staff boards with your name and logo printed directlty to the top of the display - call for details. Features and Benefits: Please double click on the above images of our acrylic staff photo boards to zoom into a more detailed view Staff photo boards provide a professioal looking wall mounted display panel for quick reference of staff / team members Choice of black, white, clear or clear frost 5mm thick acrylic back panel with polished edges. Corners are rounded with no sharp edges Clear acrylic photo pockets allow staff photos to be changed quickly and easily Supplied with 4 polished sign fittings to give that floating effect off a wall Each photo pocket size is 75mm high x 50mm wide Header panel pocket is 260mm wide x 50mm high Please see the table below for our standard sized staff photo boards. We also manufacture custom sized boards if you require different sized pockets or different quantities of pockets - please call us on 01202 480104 for further details. Staff photo board prices are detailed in the drop down menu at the top of the page. Manufactured to order in our factory in Christchurch, Dorset, UK. Please allow 5 working days for delivery Please see our stand off fittings instructions by clicking here Looking for a a more secure staff photo board which can't be tampered with? Check out our Secure Staff Photo Boards ! Looking for a staff photo board with a different coloured back panel? We have a range of colours available other than our standard colours listed! Please contact us for a quote. Looking for a staff photo board with bespoke printing and branding to suit your business? With state of the art printers, we are able to fully print or brand these staff boards with your logos and messages! If this is something you are interested in, contact us for a quote! Kuta Utara, Kabupaten Badung, Bali 80361, Indonesia Show map Finns VIP Beach Club Bali Bottle Service and VIP Table Booking With the choice of two swimming pools, two restaurants, daily DJs, a Sushi Bar, stunning sunsets, and live vocalists, Finns VIP Beach Club Bali offers a sprawling area of 170m of amazing oceanfront venue. The beach club is situated at the popular Berawa surf break. The venue is located only ten minutes from Seminyak. Visitors at the Finns VIP Beach Club can look forward to lazing away your entire day in the sun from the comfort of top-class deluxe beds. You can relax on the beauty of the white sand beach. You can also have great relaxation at the lavish party beds that are located directly in the lagoon pool. Families at the venue are catered for at the venue’s Gazebo pool. There is also the presence of the VIP oceanfront infinity pool. When you opt for Finns VIP Beach Club bottle service and VIP table booking, you will get access to its two pools and five bar areas. There is also the presence of two dedicated restaurants along with a Sushi bar, stunning sunsets, live vocalists and performances, daily DJs, and much more. You can enjoy it all with the help of Finns VIP Beach Club bottle service and VIP table booking services. You can expect the prices here to start at around IDR 1,000. Finns VIP Beach Club Bali Information What is the Address of Finns VIP Beach Club? Finns VIP Beach Club is situated at Jl. Pantai Berawa No.99, Canggu, Kec. Kuta Utara, Kabupaten Badung. What is the Price for Finns VIP Beach Club bottle service? Finns VIP Beach Club bottle service and VIP table booking will vary depending on talent spinning, the event in the club, and the total number of guests in the club. You can reach out to us to avail our bespoke luxury concierge services in Bali. What is the price for Finns VIP Beach Club VIP tables? The best tables at the day club are situated by the beach that overlooks the sea. The minimum spending for VIP table bookings here will vary on the number of guests and VIP table availability. You can also expect higher prices on special occasions. Contact us now to know more! What is the menu at Finns Club? As you would like to sit by the beach and relax, you can relish some of the most delicious cuisines from all parts of the world. At Finns VIP Beach Club, you also have access to the finest selection of drinks and cocktails. What is the Guestlist at Finns VIP Beach Club? There is an impressive lineage of the Finns VIP Beach Club. It is known for its impressive guest list from all corners of the world. As you become a part of the elite guest list of the beach club, you can think of bumping into some celebrity or famous star. There is no official guest list currently. You can keep reaching out to us for experiencing the best-ever nightlife in Bali . What is the Dress Code at Finns Club? For an optimum experience at Finns VIP Beach Club in Bali , you should be dressed in casual attire. It is recommended to follow the dress code to ensure entry into the club.
